_:Neb780aa5852f4359a33f68f098d64b10 <http://schema.org/description> "Trinity House is the General Lighthouse Authority for England, Wales, the Channel Islands and Gibraltar. It provides marine aids to navigation to assist the safe passage of mariners through waters in these areas. It also has statutory powers to mark and disperse wrecks that are a hazard to navigation. Trinity House is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Transport ." <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
